      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why im typing this. everything just feels... heavy. like i've spent 5 years building this version of myself around my research and now that the funding is gone and the lab results are a joke, there's nothing left. i'm just so incredibly tired of trying to fix things that are fundamentally broken. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to be able to rest without feeling guilty for failing.",
