    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's hard though. it's not just \"taking a break.\" when i close my eyes i dont see a vacation or a nap, i just see a permanent kind of quiet. like, the world is constantly demanding things from me and i have nothing left to give. the idea of just... not having to exist in this cycle anymore... it's the only thing that feels like actual peace.",
